					<!--cached-Mon, 14 Jul 2014 08:17:57 +0000-->Have you tried to get an xray of it to see what might be going on inside? Maybe it&#39;s a tendon thats snapping rather than the joint cracking? Then again it maybe the beginnings of arthritis and you&#39;re just not having the pain yet? Hard to say.. I&#39;d get a doc to take a thorough look at it inside and out.
					
