					<!--cached-Mon, 14 Jul 2014 08:17:57 +0000-->My thumb on my left hand does that.   Kinda crackles and eventually pops.    It&#39;s on my picking hand too.   I think it came from the way I hold my pick, but it&#39;s been doing it for years now without any real pain or anything.    Every doctor I&#39;ve ever asked has just said it&#39;s really of no concern.    My right shoulder does this too, kinda sounds like gravel being walked on when I rotate it, slightly popping.   But that&#39;s from multiple injuries to it.
					
